I was a writer at a small market TV Station in Flint Michigan.The news director walks into my tiny office one day and lets a giant fart rip, he smiles and then turns to leave and says on the way out "oh man, that one had foam on the end of it!"on another day ...The business manager walks into my office to discuss some biz. During the conversation he casually grabs a paper clip off my desk and begins to scrape the inside of his ear. As we finish our chat, he removes said paper clip, now full of ear wax, places it back on my desk and walks out.I'll never, ever forget those guys.
